{"word":"ἀναγκαστέος","slug":"ἀναγκαστέος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀναγκαστέος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:verbal Adjective'>verb. <a href='S:Adjective'>adj.</a></a> of <el>ἀναγκάζω.</el>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to be compelled</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:neuter'>neut.</a> <el>ἀναγκαστέον</el> <i>one must compel</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}